            </figcaption>

            <div class="app-demo-outer-container">
              <div class="app-demo-container section-two">
                <div>
                  <%= render partial: 'shared/iphone_silhouette' %>
                  <%= render partial: 'shared/iphone_silhouette' %>
                  <%= render partial: 'shared/iphone_silhouette' %>
                  <img src="/iphone-frame.png" alt="iphone frame for web app demo"/>
                  <video autoplay loop muted >
                    <source src="demovideo2.webm" type="video/webm">
                  </video>
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </figure>

        <figure class="section-two-right">
          <div class="figure-background">
            <svg class="figure-background-circle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle r="340" cx="350" cy="350" />
            </svg>
            <svg class="figure-background-circle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle r="240" cx="250" cy="250" />
            </svg>
            <svg class="figure-background-circle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle r="140" cx="150" cy="150" />
            </svg>

            <div class="dale-cooper-image-container section-two">
              <img src="dalecooper-image2-coloradjusted-blurred2.png" />
              <img src="dalecooper-image2-coloradjusted-blurred1.png" />
              <img src="dalecooper4-coloradjusted-blurred1.png" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="figure-inner">
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Make those audio memos professional!</h3>
              <p>Wearing a suit may be required.</p>
            </figcaption>
          </div>
        </figure>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Sales Point 3 -->
<section class="column section-spthree" id="section-spthree">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="home-section-inner">

      <div class="home-section-title-container">
        <div>
          <%= render 'shared/icons/icons_othertext' %>
          <h2>Everything Else</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
        Learn to live with the sound of your own voice.<br>
        Memos, on the fly recordings, audio diaries, murder mystery evidence contemplation - TP Memos is what you need.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="figure-container">

        <figure class="section-three-left">

          <div class="figure-inner">
            <figcaption>
              <h3>Hardware voice recorders are cool, but TP Audio Memos are more convenient!</h3>
              <p>Hardware recorder only for hardcore Twin Peaks fans.</p>
            </figcaption>

            <div class="figure-background-voice-recorder-container">
              <div class="figure-background-voice-recorder">
                <div class="blob-outer"></div>
                <div class="blob-middle"></div>
                <div class="blob-center"></div>

                <img src="vocerecorder-coloradjusted.png" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </figure>

        <figure class="section-three-right">
          <div class="figure-inner">
            <figcaption>
              <h3>It's free!</h3>
              <p>Sign up to start using it.</p>
            </figcaption>

            <div class="app-demo-outer-container">
              <div class="app-demo-container section-three">
                <div>
                  <%= link_to 'Try for Free', new_user_registration_path, class: "sign-up-button" %>
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
